00:06:19.480 --> 00:06:25.679
That comes with a lot of challenges when you need to use it in a heavily regulated environment

00:06:25.679 --> 00:06:33.119
such as pharma is, because there are a lot of rules and standards you need to squeeze

00:06:33.119 --> 00:06:41.239
down on top of your processes in order to comply with all the regulatory authorities,

00:06:41.239 --> 00:06:43.239
not only in the US, but around the world.

00:06:43.239 --> 00:06:51.399
So a lot of demands to how we actually produce code and submit code and data to authorities.

00:06:51.399 --> 00:06:54.760
