would like go through everything and had like modeling outputs.

00:15:57.359 --> 00:16:04.159
And it just seemed like such an obvious use case for us to go into a Shiny app.

00:16:04.960 --> 00:16:10.559
And that was one of the first thing that we really like sell to our stakeholders.

00:16:10.640 --> 00:16:18.799
